attacks.description:
Press Normal Attack to launch four consecutive strikes while on the ground.
First strike: Deals damage equal to 739% of ATK + 693 to targets and causes a short hitstun to those without Hyperbody;
Second strike: Deals damage equal to 1,024% of ATK + 961 to targets and slightly knocks back those without Hyperbody;
Third strike: Deals damage equal to 985% of ATK + 924 to targets and slightly knocks back those without Hyperbody;
Fourth strike: Deals damage equal to 1,387% of ATK + 1,302 to targets and knocks back those without Hyperbody.
Using Protocol Decryption's second, third, and fourth strikes grants 2 Encrypted Data if Hostile Intruder is active. Press Normal Attack during the fourth strike to cancel the attack wind-down and launch the second strike.
